title: 291: 2018 NFL Draft Preview Show
itunes:title: 291: 2018 NFL Draft Preview Show
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks preview the upcoming 2018 NFL Draft from Dallas. What buzz are the guys hearing about the first round (4:45)? Who is this season's Alvin Kamara (25:48)? Which prospect are steals on day 2 & 3 (28:28)? DJ and Bucky have you covered on this episode of Move the Sticks driven by Hyundai.
